title: Kiss Man Person Medium Light Skin Tone
alsoKnownAs: Man Kissing Man Medium Light Skin Tone
description: A man kissing another man, with medium-light skin tones. Represents romantic affection between two men.
apple_vendor_description: On Apple devices, this emoji depicts a man with a medium-light skin tone leaning in for a gentle kiss, his eyes closed in a moment of tenderness. The signature Apple design imbues the illustration with soft, rounded edges and realistic lighting, creating a subtly glossy 3D effect that emphasizes the intimate gesture. This emoji beautifully conveys affection, romance, or a sweet farewell in digital conversations.
